<p class="lead">Review Pastor Craig‚Äôs points to remember what stuck out to you from the message.</p>
<p><a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/111/mrk.2.17.niv">Mark 2:17</a> <a href="https://www.bible.com/bible/111/mrk.2.1-5.niv">Mark 2:1-5</a></p>

<p>We will do anything short of <strong>sin</strong> to reach people who don‚Äôt know <strong>Christ</strong>. To reach people no one is reaching, we‚Äôll <strong>do</strong> things no one is <strong>doing</strong>.<br />
Rate your love for people without Christ on a scale of <em>‚ÄúApathetic‚Äù</em> to <em>‚ÄúPassionate‚Äù</em>.
###Reaching People with the Love of Christ</p>
<ul>
  <li>Bear some <strong>burdens</strong>.<br />
