<h2 id="live-it-out">Live It Out</h2>
<p class="lead">End each week with a challenge to take action. Lead your group to help each person identify their next steps.</p>

<ul>
  <li>Name three people you know who need Jesus in their lives. What will you do this week to reach out to them?</li>
  <li>In what area of your life do you need to be more bold with sharing God‚Äôs love? What step will you take toward that this week?</li>
</ul>
